SUBJECT:  TYMNET ENGINE DIAGNOSTICS


               THIS BULLETIN DESCRIBES THE CURRENT DIAGNOSTICS AVAILABLE
               FOR THE TYMNET ENGINE. PLEASE BEAR IN MIND THAT SOME OF
               THESE DIAGNOSTICS WERE WRITTEN TO RESOLVE SPECIFIC DESIGN
               PROBLEMS DURING PROTOTYPE DEBUGGING AND HENCE THIS IN NO
               WAY REPRESENTS A COMPREHENSIVE DIAGNOSTIC PACKAGE.WHERE
               POSSIBLE, THESE DIAGNOSTICS HAVE BEEN MODIFIED TO A MORE
               GENERAL FIELD APPLICATION.

               ALL THE FILES LISTED BELOW ARE AVAILABLE AS FOLLOWS:-
               (MAINTDIAG:29)  AND  (MAINTDIAG:33)

ENGMEM.DOC     :ENGINE MEMORY TEST DESCRIPTION AND RUNNING INSTRUCTIONS.
ENGMEM.NAD     :ENGINE MEMORY TEST SOURCE CODE.
