3600IT.LST     :3600 BAUD INTERRUPT TEST LISTING.
ENGMFT.DOC     :MULTIFUNCTION CARD FAT-FINGER TEST.
SYASV3.DOC     :SYNC/ASYNC TEST INSTRUCTIONS.
SYASV3.NAD     :SYNC/ASYNC TEST SOURCE CODE.
SYASV3.NIB     :SYNC/ASYNC TEST BINARY IMAGE FOR DOWNSTREAM LOADING.
